reviewText:
+ Great graphics;
+ Great gameplay;
+ Roster always up-to-date;

- Terrible customization (paying for apparel with stat points???);
- Spike Lee joint so bad can't even enjoy ironically;
- UI gives me headaches;
- Spend more time on loading screens than playing;

Didn't pay a cent, so no harm done. However this is not the basketball game you're looking for.

6/10
